from bird_service import BirdClient

client = BirdClient()
response = await client.list_birds(ListBirdsInput(genus="corvus"))
assert response == ListBirdsOutput(birds=[
    Bird(
        order="passiformes",
        family="corvidae",
        genus="corvus",
        species="cornix",
        common_names={
            "en_US": ["Hooded Crow"],
            "de_DE": ["Nebelkrähe"],
        },
    ),
])

from bird_service import BirdClient

client = BirdClient(protocol=RestJson1Protocol())
response = await client.list_birds(ListBirdsInput(genus="corvus"))
assert response == ListBirdsOutput(birds=[
    Bird(
        order="passiformes",
        family="corvidae",
        genus="corvus",
        species="cornix",
        common_names={
            "en_US": ["Hooded Crow"],
            "de_DE": ["Nebelkrähe"],
        },
    ),
])
